    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_Soap_Client class does not allow the SoapClient option 'exceptions' to be changed. Further to this, it doesn't actually enable it by default, meaning that if there's a SoapFault then a fatal error is thrown.</p>

